Title: generate_series
Feature: generate_series ( start timestamp, stop timestamp, step interval ) → setof timestamp
generate_series ( start timestamp with time zone, stop timestamp with time zone, step interval [, timezone text ] ) → setof timestamp with time zone
Description: Generates a series of values from start to stop, with a step size of step. In the timezone-aware form, times of day and daylight-savings adjustments are computed according to the time zone named by the timezone argument, or the current TimeZone setting if that is omitted.
